Installation
------------

Flush can be installed in two ways:

Run directly from untar directory:
 $ ./configure && make
 $ sudo make install

OR (for debian-based distributives)

 $ dpkg-buildpackage -rfakeroot
 $ sudo dpkg -i ../flush*.deb
 

Dependencies
------------

 * libboost 1.34-1.38
 * libconfig-1.3
 * libgtkmm-2.4
 * libtorrent-rasterbar 0.14 

